#
# Captures the current KDE Plasma window layout to a YAML file.
# System windows (plasmashell, ibus, etc.) are excluded by default.
#
# The captured layout is always printed to stdout as YAML so you can
# review it immediately.  Use --dry-run to skip saving to disk.
#
# USAGE:
#   python3 kwin_snapshot.py [OPTIONS]
#
# OPTIONS:
#   --output FILE     Write snapshot to FILE
#                     (default: ~/.config/wayland-desktop/snapshots/YYYY-MM-DD_HHMM.yaml)
#   --include-system  Include compositor/system windows in snapshot
#   --config FILE     Use alternate config file
#                     (default: ~/.config/wayland-desktop/config.yaml)
#   --show-config     Print loaded aliases and exit
#   --dry-run         Print snapshot YAML to stdout without saving to disk
